<item>
            <title>[LU-18466] code glitch in MDD transaction retry</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18466</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;  There could be several declaration in one transaction, so that lod_object has been saved in previous declaration, we need to update the lod_object&apos;s layout generation in later declarations in the transacation, not return error.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="85937">LU-18466</key>
            <summary>code glitch in MDD transaction retry</summary>
